criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age ≥ 18 years;

          -  Informed Consent;

          -  >1 year after transplantation

          -  Medical approvement for participation in the study by the nephrologist.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Psychopathology;

          -  Severe cognitive disorders;

          -  Negative advice of the nephrologist and/or cardiologist.
